4013:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   Description of ADC group regular sequencer features:
4014:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - For devices with sequencer fully configurable
4015:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           (function "LL_ADC_REG_SetSequencerRanks()" available):
4016:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           sequencer length and each rank affectation to a channel
4017:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           are configurable.
4018:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           This function performs configuration of:
4019:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           - Sequence length: Number of ranks in the scan sequence.
4020:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           - Sequence direction: Unless specified in parameters, sequencer
4021:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             scan direction is forward (from rank 1 to rank n).
4022:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           Sequencer ranks are selected using
4023:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           function "LL_ADC_REG_SetSequencerRanks()".
4024:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - For devices with sequencer not fully configurable
4025:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           (function "LL_ADC_REG_SetSequencerChannels()" available):
4026:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           sequencer length and each rank affectation to a channel
