4028:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           This function performs configuration of:
4029:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           - Sequence length: Number of ranks in the scan sequence is
4030:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             defined by number of channels set in the sequence,
4031:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             rank of each channel is fixed by channel HW number.
4032:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             (channel 0 fixed on rank 0, channel 1 fixed on rank1, ...).
4033:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           - Sequence direction: Unless specified in parameters, sequencer
4034:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             scan direction is forward (from lowest channel number to
4035:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             highest channel number).
4036:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           Sequencer ranks are selected using
