5097:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         cannot be used):
5098:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         Refer to function @ref LL_ADC_INJ_SetQueueMode().
5099:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   In the contexts queue, only the active context can be read.
5100:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         The parameters of this function can be read using functions:
5101:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         @arg @ref LL_ADC_INJ_GetTriggerSource()
