5352:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h **** /**
5353:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @brief  Set sampling time of the selected ADC channel
5354:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         Unit: ADC clock cycles.
5355:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   On this device, sampling time is on channel scope: independently
5356:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         of channel mapped on ADC group regular or injected.
5357:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   In case of internal channel (VrefInt, TempSensor, ...) to be
ARM GAS  C:\Users\ChipTec\AppData\Local\Temp\ccMHUsU7.s 			page 96


5358:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         converted:
5359:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         sampling time constraints must be respected (sampling time can be
5360:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         adjusted in function of ADC clock frequency and sampling time
5361:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         setting).
5362:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         Refer to device datasheet for timings values (parameters TS_vrefint,
5363:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         TS_temp, ...).
5364:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   Conversion time is the addition of sampling time and processing time.
5365:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         On this STM32 series, ADC processing time is:
5366:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - 12.5 ADC clock cycles at ADC resolution 12 bits
5367:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - 10.5 ADC clock cycles at ADC resolution 10 bits
5368:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - 8.5 ADC clock cycles at ADC resolution 8 bits
5369:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - 6.5 ADC clock cycles at ADC resolution 6 bits
5370:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   In case of ADC conversion of internal channel (VrefInt,
5371:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         temperature sensor, ...), a sampling time minimum value
