5672:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h **** /**
5673:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @brief  Set ADC analog watchdog monitored channels:
5674:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         a single channel, multiple channels or all channels,
5675:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         on ADC groups regular and-or injected.
5676:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   Once monitored channels are selected, analog watchdog
5677:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         is enabled.
5678:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   In case of need to define a single channel to monitor
