6220:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         (availability of ADC group injected depends on STM32 series).
6221:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   If both groups regular and injected are selected,
6222:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         specify behavior of ADC group injected interrupting
6223:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         group regular: when ADC group injected is triggered,
6224:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         the oversampling on ADC group regular is either
6225:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         temporary stopped and continued, or resumed from start
