6277:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - continuous mode (all conversions of oversampling ratio
6278:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           are done from 1 trigger)
6279:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - discontinuous mode (each conversion of oversampling ratio
