1125:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *         Occurrence of flag JEOS rising:
1126:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *          - If sequencer is composed of 1 rank, flag JEOS is equivalent
1127:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *            to flag JEOC.
1128:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *          - If sequencer is composed of several ranks, during the scan
1129:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *            sequence flag JEOC only is raised, at the end of the scan sequence
1130:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *            both flags JEOC and EOS are raised.
1131:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *         Flag JEOS must not be cleared by this function because
1132:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *         it would not be compliant with low power features
1133:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *         (feature low power auto-wait, not available on all STM32 series).
1134:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *         To clear this flag, either use function:
1135:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *         in programming model IT: @ref HAL_ADC_IRQHandler(), in programming
1136:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *         model polling: @ref HAL_ADCEx_InjectedPollForConversion()
1137:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *         or @ref __HAL_ADC_CLEAR_FLAG(&hadc, ADC_FLAG_JEOS).
1138:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   * @param hadc ADC handle
1139:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   * @param InjectedRank the converted ADC injected rank.
1140:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *          This parameter can be one of the following values:
1141:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *            @arg @ref ADC_INJECTED_RANK_1 ADC group injected rank 1
1142:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *            @arg @ref ADC_INJECTED_RANK_2 ADC group injected rank 2
1143:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *            @arg @ref ADC_INJECTED_RANK_3 ADC group injected rank 3
