1615:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****  ===============================================================================
1616:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****     [..]  This section provides functions allowing to:
1617:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****       (+) Configure channels on injected group
1618:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****       (+) Configure multimode when multimode feature is available
1619:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****       (+) Enable or Disable Injected Queue
