1621:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****       (+) Enter ADC deep-power-down mode
1622:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_adc_ex.c **** 
1623:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_adc_ex.c **** @endverbatim
